text: On 26 February 2018, the Alex Jones conspiracy trolling network http://Infowars.com reported that an emergency responder to the Valentine’s Day mass shooting at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School in Parkland, FL said they were “told to stand down” https://www.snopes.com/did-first-responder-stand-down-parkland/ …pic.twitter.com/04DRkenLfW
